Clair Obscur Expedition 33 Monoco Guide -  How to Play Monoco (Build Tips)
In this Clair Obscur Expedition 33 guide, we break down Monoco’s best skills, weapons, and strategies to maximize his effectiveness in battle. Learn how to properly use the Bestial Wheel to your advantage and use high-damage combos to dominate enemies. Whether you're looking for solo builds, counter-based strategies, or team synergies, this guide will help you optimize Monoco for boss fights, exploration, and late-game encounters.
